        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Custom permissions assigned to guest users may bypass standard sharing logic and trigger privileged Apex code paths, expanding the attack surface for unauthenticated users.</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Remediation__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Remove all custom permissions from guest profiles. Only assign custom permissions to authenticated Experience Cloud members who have an explicit documented need.</value>
